- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses improving RL algorithms. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper discusses Multi-Goal RL and Hindsight Experience Replay. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is less likely but still possible as the tasks involve object manipulation. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also less likely but relevant as the tasks involve control of robotic systems.
